{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Regina ?] came to our house, and she said that on the outskirt of town there is a Russian prison camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because as the Russians were retreating, they caught some Russians and kept them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a prison camp, barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're looking for girls to peel potatoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the end of the day, they give us bread and marmalade and a ration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was excited-- do you want to come?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came-- we were able to-- after 4:00, we were not allowed, but in the daytime we were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was sacks of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a German kitchen for the German personnel, kitchen for the prisoner, the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were under barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, they load them on trucks and took them on highways-- there were many [? bombed-out ?] [INAUDIBLE] -- to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then under guard, they brought them back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were all-- some of them had sores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they still had their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after a few days, I had sores from the knives, so I bandaged my fingers, peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German cook was always angry that we are not doing a good job, yelling at us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we ate the soup the prisoners ate, which was-- they didn't even-- with some vegetables.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't even wash the vegetables.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were worms floating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But at the end of the day, we got bread, a small jar of marmalade, some margarine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I felt good that I'm providing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm bringing home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES] We saw-- the prisoners were like by the wire, standing around, hanging around in the yard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the German passed, when they smoked a cigarette, they just threw their butts down.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
